Sentencas: Dual-phase composites of (1-x)La0.5Sr0.5CoO3-delta/xLaSrCoO(4 +/-delta) were designed and evaluated as the cathode materials of solid-oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Hetero-structured La0.5Sr0.5CoO3-δ/LaSrCoO4±δ cathode with high electro-catalytic activity for solid-oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The composites were prepared by one-pot method and X-ray diffraction results reveal good compatibility in structure between these two phases.
Titulo: Hetero-structured La0.5Sr0.5CoO3-δ/LaSrCoO4±δ cathode with high electro-catalytic activity for solid-oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: It was also found the lattice thermal expansions of each phase constituent is greatly suppressed, and this means that the thermal expansion coefficient of the composite matches better with the electrolyte of solid-oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Hetero-structured La0.5Sr0.5CoO3-δ/LaSrCoO4±δ cathode with high electro-catalytic activity for solid-oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity of the composite is favorable but its thermal-activated transport mechanism is rather complex.
Titulo: Hetero-structured La0.5Sr0.5CoO3-δ/LaSrCoO4±δ cathode with high electro-catalytic activity for solid-oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Compared with each single phase, both area specific resistance and overpotential of the composite cathodes are greatly reduced.
Titulo: Hetero-structured La0.5Sr0.5CoO3-δ/LaSrCoO4±δ cathode with high electro-catalytic activity for solid-oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: For the x = 0.25 composite cathode along with the supporting La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.83Mg0.17O2.815 electrolyte and Ni-Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 anode, the maximum power density of 920 mW cm(-2) at 800 degrees C is achieved from the single cell fed with pure H-2 fuel.
Titulo: Hetero-structured La0.5Sr0.5CoO3-δ/LaSrCoO4±δ cathode with high electro-catalytic activity for solid-oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Our work demonstrates that such dual-phase composites are quite more promising than each single phase as cathode materials for solid-oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Hetero-structured La0.5Sr0.5CoO3-δ/LaSrCoO4±δ cathode with high electro-catalytic activity for solid-oxide fuel cells
